## Amazon Lex
1.	Select the location (Oregon)
2.	On search bar type “Amazon Lex”
3.	Click on Get started
4.	Select custom bot; To create your own bot. 
5.	On the same window of the step 4, start to fill in Bot name, language, choose output voice, session timeout, Sentiment analysis, Select yes for COPPA (Online Privacy protection)
6.	Select create.
7.	Click on create intent (Give a unique name for the new intent) 

## Complete the Steps for the editor:
8.	Fill the Sample utterances
9.	Slots (Customers information’s for delivery)
10.	 Following AWS instructor to create your own slot types.
11.	Check the confirmation prompt. 
12.	Custom confirm and cancel messages. 
13.	Add the response message.
14.	 Click on save intent.
15.	Click on Build. (For Testing)
16.	Start the Chatbot test
